		cnEcGetMemory.  Also added the following new method to Node:
		
			o cnEcGetServerMemory(pTotalMemory:Integer output; pAvailableMemory:Integer output) serverExecution;
		
		This is a server-execution version of the Node::cnEcGetMemory method.
		
