		for Unicode, and to call the appropriate External Function.
		
		Renamed the cnEcCreateDirectory External Function as				cnwdad1 21/01/2002
		cnEcCreateDirectoryA, and added a new function called cnEcCreateDirectoryW.
		
		Renamed the cnEcCreateFile External Function as	cnEcCreateFileA,	cnwdad1 21/01/2002
		and added a new function called cnEcCreateFileW.
		
