==========================================================================================
2.5.03	Changed the CnEcXMLClassFormatMaint::sampleClick method to check	cnwdad1 07/03/2002
		whether the Class being used for the sample was found, and also whether an
		instance of that class exists.  If either check fails, then an error message
		dialog (message box) is displayed.
		
		Fixed the CnEcCurrencyBox and CnEcNumericBox custom controls.		cnwdad1 12/03/2002
		The lostFocus event was supposed to convert the contents of the textboxes into a
		currency or numeric format, but this was not being done correctly (the value was
		being formatted as a plain numeric value instead).
		
		Fixed the CnEcCurrencyBox and CnEcNumericBox custom controls.		cnwdad1 13/03/2002
		The "text" mapping method wasn't checking whether the CurrencyFormat or the
		Numeric Format reference was set, which resulted in 1090 exceptions within
		the Painter.  Also added checks in the "gotFocus" event methods for a selecton
		style of "All" - if this option is set, then the contents will be selected
		after the newly formatted contents are set.  This is necessary because we're
		switching from an alphanumeric textbox to a numeric textbox.
		
		Changed the Class::cnEcGetImplementationSchema() method to now use	cnwdad1 27/03/2002
		the Type::rootType() method (much more efficient).
		
		Patched the CnEcRateGraphDriver class and associated External		cnwdad1 05/04/2002
		Functions to correct a problem where the X and Y Axis text was not being
		correctly drawn for a thin client node.
		
		Added the following method to the Date Primitive:					cnwdad1 09/04/2002
		
			o cnEcDaysInYear():Integer;
		
		Added the following method to the Integer Primitive:				cnwdad1 09/04/2002
		
			o cnEcIsBetween(pLowerValue:Integer; pUpperValue:Integer):Boolean;
		
		Added the following methods to the Global class:					cnwdad1 09/04/2002
		
			o cnEcSoundexIndigenousAustralia(pName:String):String;
			o cnEcValidateMedicareNumber(pCardNumber:String):Boolean;
	
		Changed the app.cnEcNotImplemented method to fetch the second		cnwdad1 22/04/2002
		element of the call stack instead of the first.
		
		Fixed two methods of the FileNode class:							cnwdad1 08/05/2002
			1. cnEcFileExt - if the node name had no extension, then the name of the node was being
			returned (fro the 2nd character onwards).
			
			2. cnEcFileStem - if the node name had no extension, then nothing was being returned.
		
		Changed the CnEcProgress form's load event by removing the setting	cnwdad1 08/05/2002
		of the "alwaysOnTop" flag because, if an application had cause to show a dialog box, then
		the dialog would appear beneath this progress form, and couldn't be OK'd.
		
		Changed the userDecimals attribute of the CnEcNumericBox class to	cnwdad1 19/05/2002
		be enterable by developers so that the decimal places setting is not lost when switching
		between alphanumeric and numeric modes.
		
		Changed the set up of the myNumberFormat on the CnEcNumericBox		cnwdad1 24/06/2002
		class from using the application's NumberFormat object to using a specifically created
		user-format. Needed because multiple instances of the control on one form, with different
		user-decimal values require their own NumberFormat object.
		
		Added the cnEcStripDecimalZeros method to the Decimal Primitive.	cnwdad1 27/07/2002
		Strips all trailing zeros following the decimal point.  If no decimal point is found,
		then the whole value is return.
		
		Added the cnEcStripDecimalZeros method to the String Primitive.		cnwdad1 27/07/2002
		Strips all trailing zeros following the decimal point.  If no decimal point is found,
		then the whole value is return.
		
		Added the isStripDecimalZeros property to the CnEcNumericBox		cnwdad1 27/07/2002
		control.
		
		Added the isStripDecimalZeros property to the CnEcNumericLabel		cnwdad1 27/07/2002
		control.
		
		Added the CnEcSoundexAustralia class, and removed the following		cnwdad1 06/082002
		method from the Global class:
		
			o cnEcSoundexIndigenousAustralia(pName:String):String;
		
		Added the abstract CnEcAccountCard class.							cnwdad1 06/082002
		
		Added the CnEcMedicareCard class, and removed the following method	cnwdad1 06/082002
		from the Global class:
		
			o cnEcValidateMedicareNumber(pCardNumber:String):Boolean;
		
		Added a destructor method to the CnEcHubble class to purge all		cnwdad1 08/08/2002
		instances of the "CnEcClassPropertyColls" class.  Also changed the CnEcHubble::
		getThePropertyCollection method to instantiate the "CnEcClassPropertyColls" class as
		transient objects.
		
		Added the isTagDataOnGroup attribute to the CnEcXmlParser class.	cnwdad1 08/08/2002
		This attribute can be set by calling the CnEcXmlParser::SetIsTagDataOnGroup method.
		When the flag is true, then Group structure instances will also contain tag data, when
		false, the tag data will be ignored for Group structures.
		
		Changed the CnEcHubble::initializeMe() method to set the			cnwdad1 08/08/2002
		CnEcHubble::isTagDataOnGroup property to true, to allow the XMLUtility application to
		use tag data on Group structure instances.
		
		Fixed the CnEcCsvFile::cnEcLoadCsvFile method which was showing and	cnwdad1 12/08/2002
		updating the progress form unconditionally.  Added a test of the pShowProgress parameter
		before showing or updating the progress form.
		
