			o cnEcGetParameters():ParameterColl;
		
		Added the following method to the Type class:						cnwdad1 05/04/2005
			o cnEcGetMaxLength():Integer;
		
		Added the following method to the Global class:						cnwdad1 05/04/2005
			o cnEcGetRandomColor():Integer;
		
		Added the following method to the Class class:						cnwdad1 07/04/2005
			o cnEcGetAllSuperclasses(pAllClassesObj:ClassSet input);
