			o cnEcGetReturnType():Type;
		
		Added the following method to the Collection class:					cnwdad1 19/04/2005
			o cnEcMove(pTargetCollObj:Collection input):Boolean updating;
		
		Added the following method to the Date primitive:					cnwdad1 05/05/2005
			o cnEcIsNotValid():Boolean;
		
		Renamed the CnEcDesignTable::getCollection method to				cnwdad1 23/05/2005
		cnEcGetCollection, due to a conflict with the new Table::getCollection method in JADE 6.1.
		
		Added the following method to the Table class:						cnwdad1 22/06/2005
			o cnEcExportToCSV(pFileObj:File io):Boolean updating;
		
		Changed the CnEcAppGridAppLabel::moveAppInfo and					cnwdad1 24/06/2005
		CnEcDesignTable::windowCreated methods to use the Control::convertFormPosition method
		instead of the de-implemented Form::controlToForm method.
		
