			o cnEcResetFormChangedFlag() updating, protected;
		
		Added the following methods to the Table class:						cnwdad1 30/03/2006
			o cnEcClearAllCellObjects(pIsDelete:Boolean) updating;
			o cnEcClearAllColumnObjects(pIsDelete:Boolean) updating;
			o cnEcClearAllRowObjects(pIsDelete:Boolean) updating;
			o cnEcClearColumnCellObjects(pColumn:Integer; pIsDelete:Boolean) updating;
			o cnEcClearRowCellObjects(pRow:Integer; pIsDelete:Boolean) updating;
		
		Changed the GBaseSchema::cnEcDocumentModel method so that the		cnwdad1 04/04/2006
		dynamic dictionary of sorted classes is now case-sensitive.
		
		Added the following methods to the Label class:						cnwdad1 05/04/2006
			o cnEcCenterOnParentHorizontal() updating;
		
		Fixed a problem with the CnEcDateBox control where the self.date	cnwdad1 07/04/2006
		was not being set in the lostFocus method, so the user always had to use the pop-up
		date-picker to set the date.  Also added a property called "isShowErrorMsg".  If this
		is true (can be set in the Painter or programatically) an error message will be shown
		if an invalid date was entered.  Also commented out the reset of the receiver's text
		where an invalid date has been entered.
		
		Added the following method to Global:								cnwdad1 19/04/2006
			o cnEcGetServerIniFileName():String serverExecution;
		
		Added the following method to the Process class:					cnwdad1 19/04/2006
			o cnEcGetDisplay():String;
		
		Added the following method to the Integer primitive:				cnwdad1 06/05/2006
			o cnEcOrdinalWord():String;
		
		Fixed the following methods on the TimeStamp primitive to handle	cnwdad1 06/05/2006
		more than a day's worth of time units, thus adjusting the date accordingly:
			o cnEcAddHours(pHours:Integer):TimeStamp;
			o cnEcAddMinutes(pMinutes:Integer):TimeStamp;
			o cnEcAddSeconds(pSeconds:Integer):TimeStamp;
		
		Added the following new methods:									cnwdad1 19/05/2006
			o ListBox::cnEcIsInScrollZone(pXPos:Real; pYPos:Real):Boolean;
			o Table::cnEcIsInScrollZone(pXPos:Real; pYPos:Real):Boolean;
			o TextBox::cnEcIsInScrollZone(pXPos:Real; pYPos:Real):Boolean;
		
		Promoted the Form::cnEcGetUserInput method to the Window class.		cnwdad1 22/05/2006
		
		Added the following methods to the System class:					cnwdad1 09/06/2006
			o cnEcGetMachineMemoryAppServ():Integer;
			o cnEcGetMachineMemoryClient():Integer;
			o cnEcGetMachineMemoryServer():Integer serverExecution;
			o cnEcGetNoOfProcessorsAppServ():Integer;
			o cnEcGetNoOfProcessorsClient():Integer;
			o cnEcGetNoOfProcessorsServer():Integer serverExecution;
		
		Added the following external function in the Shell32 library:		cnwdad1 10/06/2006
			o cnEcShellExecute(	pHandle:Integer;
								pOperation:String;
								pFileName:String;
								pParameters:String;
								pDirectory:String;
								pShowHow:Integer):Integer is ShellExecuteA in shell32;
		
		Added the following methods to the Binary primitive type:			cnwdad1 10/06/2006
			o cnEcCopyToTempFile(pFileName:String; pFileTS:TimeStamp):Boolean;
			o cnEcPrintMe(pFileName:String; pFileTS:TimeStamp; pFormHandle:Integer):Boolean;
			o cnEcViewMe(pFileName:String; pFileTS:TimeStamp; pFormHandle:Integer):Boolean;
		
		Added the following method to the ListBox class:					cnwdad1 17/06/2006
			o cnEcOpenFirstNode():Boolean;
		
		Added the following method to the String primitive:					cnwdad1 15/08/2006
			o cnEcStripAmpersands():String;
		
		Added the following method to the Label class:						cnwdad1 15/08/2006
			o cnEcStripAmpersands() updating;
		
		Added the following methods to the Table class:						cnwdad1 15/09/2006
			o cnEcFirstColumn():Integer;
			o cnEcFirstRow():Integer;
		
		Added thenfollowing method to the TimeStamp primitive:				cnwdad1 21/09/2006
			o cnEcMidPoint(pTimeStamp:TimeStamp):TimeStamp;
		
		Added the following method to the CharacterArray class:				cnwdad1 02/10/2006
			o cnEcLoadFromString(pString:String) updating;
		
		Added the following method to the Table class:						cnwdad1 19/10/2006
			o cnEcAddItem(pValue:String; pItemObj:Object) updating;
		
		Added the following method to the Table control:					cnwdad1 19/10/2006
			o cnEcBoolean(pRowPointer:Integer; pColPointer:Integer):Boolean;
		
		Changed the CnEcEmailForm form to allow the email subject and body	cnwdad1 10/01/2007
		to be pre-set when the form is loaded.
		
		Changed the signature of following method on the Binary Primitive	cnwdad1 19/01/2007
		so that the file name parameter is now IO:
			o cnEcReadFromFile(pFileName:String io):Boolean updating;
		
		Changed the following method on the Binary Primitive so that if	a	cnwdad1 19/01/2007
		full file name is passed in as a parameter, thenstrip out the path name, leaving just
		the file name:
			o cnEcCopyToTempFile(pFileName:String; pFileTS:TimeStamp):Boolean;
		
		Added the following methods to the ComboBox and ListBox classes:	cnwdad1 12/01/2007
			o cnEcAddItemDataObject(pNewItem:String; pItemData:Integer; pItemObject:Object):Integer;
			o cnEcAddItemDataObjectAt(pIndex:Integer; pNewItem:String; pItemData:Integer; pItemObject:Object):Boolean;
		
		Added the following method to the Table control class:				cnwdad1 22/02/2007
			o cnEcIsValidColumn(pColPointer:Integer):Boolean;
		
		Added the following method to the Integer primitive Type:			cnwdad1 26/02/2007
			o cnEcTableCheckBoxValue():Boolean;
		
		Added the following methods to the TimeStamp primitive Type:		cnwdad1 06/03/2007
			o cnEcIsGreaterThan(pTimeStamp:TimeStamp):Boolean;
			o cnEcIsGreaterThanOrEqual(pTimeStamp:TimeStamp):Boolean;
			o cnEcIsLessThan(pTimeStamp:TimeStamp):Boolean;

==========================================================================================
3.0.07	Added the following methods to the SchemaEntity class:				cnwdad1 23/03/2007
			o cnEcSetText(pText:String) updating;
			o cnEcSetUserText(pText:String) updating;
		
		Changed the CnEcDatabaseAdmin::backupAllDatabaseFiles and 			cnwdad1 08/05/2007
		JadeScript::cnwdad1_DoBackup methods to replace an invalid character (En Dash = hex 96)
		with a normal hyphen (hex 2D).  The character was preventing an ANSI extract from being
		loaded into a Unicode develeopment environment (refer to Jade PAR #43889).
		
		Added the following methods to the Table control:					cnwdad1 24/05/2007
			o cnEcResort(pColumnList:ParamListType):Boolean;
			o cnEcSetSortAsc(pSortOptionList:ParamListType):Boolean;
			o cnEcSetSortCased(pSortOptionList:ParamListType):Boolean;
			o cnEcSetSortTypes(pSortTypeList:ParamListType):Boolean;
		
		Added the following method to the String primitive:					cnwdad1 13/06/2007
			o cnEcGetPathOfFileName():String;
		
		Added the following methods to Global (GBaseSchema):				cnwdad1 13/06/2007
			o cnEcEditTextFile(pFileName:String):Integer;
			o cnEcExploreDirectory(pPathName:String):Integer;
			o cnEcOpenFile(pFileName:String):Integer;
			o cnEcOpenIExplorer(pURL:String):Integer;
			o cnEcOpenMSExcel(pFileName:String):Integer;
			o cnEcOpenMSWord(pFileName:String):Integer;
			o cnEcPrintFile(pFileName:String):Integer;
			o cnEcSendEmail(pEmailAddress:String):Integer;
		
		Added the following primitive methods:								cnwdad1 13/06/2007
			o Date::cnEcAddWeeks(pWeeks:Integer):Date;
			o TimeStamp::cnEcAddWeeks(pWeeks:Integer):TimeStamp;
		
		Fixed CnEcBaseException::errorItem mapping method to truncate the	cnwdad1 15/06/2007
		error message if its length exceeds the maximum length of the errorItem property.  If
		the error message is truncated, the flag property "isErrorTruncated" will be set to true
		and the "fullMessage" property (max length) will be set to the original errorItem value.
		
		Added an exception handler to the CnEcDateMask::cnEcDate method to	cnwdad1 21/06/2007
		to handle the case where the getTextAsDate method can throw an exception.
		
		Added the following method to the FileFolder class:					cnwdad1 22/06/2007
			o cnEcGetSize(pIsNested:Boolean):Decimal updating;
		
		Added the following method to the Table class:						cnwdad1 13/10/2007
			o cnEcAlternateRowColors(pColor1:Integer; pColor2:Integer) updating;
		
		Added the following methods to the GBaseSchema (Global) class:		cnwdad1 19/11/2007
			o cnEcReadBinaryFile(pFileName:String):Binary;
		
		Added the following method to the Table control class:				cnwdad1 30/11/2007
			o cnEcSetSelectedForObject(pObject:Object):Boolean updating;
		
		Added the following method to the File class to read a file in		cnwdad1 20/12/2007
		chunks rather than as one BLOB:
			o cnEcReadBinary(pSize:Integer):Binary;
		
		Added the following method to the Table control class:				cnwdad1 21/12/2007
			o cnEcGetRowString(pRowPointer:Integer):String;
		
		Fixed layout problem with CnEcPrintTableForm where, when printing	cnwdad1 22/12/2007
		a Table Control in landscape, the report was not making full use of the available
		page width.  Also tidied up overall layout and added header and footer line rules.
		
		Fixed a bug in the ListBox::cnEcExpandItem method where an open		cnwdad1 23/12/2007
		node would close, and fail to expand the remainder of the tree if that option was requested.
		
		Added the following methods to the CnEcCalendarControl class:		cnwdad1 06/05/2008
			o doAddEvent(pEventObj:CnEcCalendarEvent input; pIsHighlight:Boolean):Boolean updating;
			o doDeleteSpecificEvent(pEventObj:CnEcCalendarEvent io):Boolean;
			o getEventObjectsForDate(pDate:Date; pAllEventsObj:CnEcCalendarEventArray input);
		
		Added the following features to the CnEcCalendarEvent class:		cnwdad1 06/05/2008
			Properties:
			o eventTime (Time)
			o isRepeating (Boolean)
			o repeatEvery (Integer)
			o repeatTerm (Integer)
			o repeatTimes (Integer)
			
			Constants:
			o REPEAT_DAY (Integer)
			o REPEAT_DAY_STR (String);
			o REPEAT_MONTH (Integer)
			o REPEAT_MONTH_STR (String);
			o REPEAT_WEEK (Integer)
			o REPEAT_WEEK_STR (String);
			o REPEAT_YEAR (Integer)
			o REPEAT_YEAR_STR (String);
			
			Methods:
			o getProxy(): SelfType;
			o isRepeatInRange(pDateFrom:Date; pDateTo:Date):Boolean updating;
			o setEventTime(pTime:Time) updating;
			o setRepeat(pIsRepeat:Boolean; pRepeatEvery:Integer; pRepeatTerm:Integer; pRepeatTimes:Integer) updating;
			o updateMe(pProxyObj: SelfType) updating;
		
		Added the following abstract methods to the CnEcUnitOfMeasure		cnwdad1 10/05/2008
		class:
			o getAllUnits(pAllUnits:IntegerArray input) abstract;
			o getUnitName(pUnit:Integer):String abstract;
		
		These methods are reimplemented on each subclass.
		
		Added the following method to the BaseSchema class (i.e. App):		cnwdad1 28/05/2008
			o cnEcXhandlerInvalidRef(pExceptionObj:Exception; pObject:Object; pIsInvalid:Boolean io):Integer;
		
		Fixed the String::cnEcIsNumeric() method to use the native			cnwdad1 06/06/2008
		"String::isReal()" method.
		
		Fixed the following issues with the CnEcSpellCheck class:			cnwdad1 07/06/2008
			o When adding or editing a word to the dictionary, check if the word already exists.
			o The checkProse method was leaking multiple instances of two StringArrays.
			o When fetching alternate Soundex and Metaphone word, they arrays are now cleared rather than purged.
		
		Fixed the TextBox::cnEcDoSpellCheck method to only check if the		cnwdad1 07/06/2008
		updated text can fit in the textbox if the maxLength property is greater than zero.
		
==========================================================================================
3.0.08	Added the following methods to the JadeRichText class:				cnwdad1 04/07/2008
			o cnEcLoadFromFile(pFileName:String; pReplaceOption:Integer; pFormat:Integer; pErrorMsg:String output):Integer;
		This method will arm an exception handler before loading the RTF file to trap any errors.
		
		Fixed the CnEcXMLFormatsMaint::deleteFormat method where a 1201		cnwdad1 08/07/2008
		excepation was raised because of a recursive reference.</text>
    <ConstantCategory name="BaseSchema_Notifications" id="2b424e18-c96b-4e11-8de2-d91f4dd9da30"/>
    <ConstantCategory name="CnEcBaseException" id="e33a4093-363d-4fdf-89bc-96adec184733">
        <text>This category contains BaseSchema Exception Message codes.  The following
is a list of the code value ranges.  These exceptions will be raised with
the CnEcBaseException class.

BaseSchema Applications
=======================
01000 - 01199	BaseBackApp
01200 - 01399	BaseMethodGenerator
01400 - 01599	BaseSchemaMonitor
01600 - 01799	BaseWebTest
01800 - 01999	HCSadmin
02000 - 02199	HCSconfigure
02200 - 02399	HCSsetupWizard
02400 - 02599	IniEditor
02600 - 02799	JDBrowser
02800 - 02999	XMLUtility
03000 - 03199	BaseDocModel

BaseSchema Components
=====================
10000 - 11999	CnEcAgent
12000 - 13999	CnEcBaseEntity (general)
14000 - 15999	CnEcDataValue
16000 - 16999	CnEcLincSystemEntities
17000 - 18999	CnEcReportEntity
19000 - 19999	CnEcSerialInterface
20000 - 20999	CnEcSortEntity
21000 - 21999	CnEcXML
22000 - 23999	CnEcHtmlEntity

JADE Entities
=============
70000 - 71999	Application class
72000 - 73999	Collection classes
74000 - 75999	Connection classes
76000 - 77999	Control classes
78000 - 78999	Exception class
79000 - 79999	FileNode classes
80000 - 81999	Form classes
82000 - 82999	Global class
83000 - 84999	Primitive classes
85000 - 85999	Printer classes
86000 - 87999	SchemaEntity classes
88000 - 88999	System class
89000 - 89999	WebSession class</text>
    </ConstantCategory>
